response.overview: Hbomberguy takes you on a journey to discover the origin of the Roblox Oof sound. Find out all about Tommy Tallarico, the veritable video game industry icon, along the way.
response.tagline: What is the Roblox Oof? Where did the Roblox Oof come from? Who made the Roblox Oof? Where am I, Roblox Oof? Can you help me?
